<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF2B6A94F7F397481933B9D1" pageId="208" pageNumber="970" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF2B6A94F7F397481933B9D1" blockId="208.[2063,2655,273,700]" lastBlockId="208.[1447,2658,710,3344]" pageId="208" pageNumber="970">
Subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF2B6A94F759974816F9BA00" authority="Kaup, 1829" box="[2213,2297,273,306]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="208" pageNumber="970" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Myotis</taxonomicName>
; 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF2B6A94F6F297481788BA00" baseAuthorityName="Temminck" baseAuthorityYear="1840" box="[2318,2440,273,306]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="208" pageNumber="970" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="horsfieldii">horsfieldii</taxonomicName>
species group. 
<collectingRegion id="0650F81CFF2B6A94F7F39760163EBA68" box="[2063,2110,313,346]" country="South Sudan" name="Lakes" pageId="208" pageNumber="970">See</collectingRegion>
M. ridley: and 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF2B6A94F6F3976017B7BA68" baseAuthorityName="Gould" baseAuthorityYear="1854" box="[2319,2487,313,346]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="208" pageNumber="970" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="macropus">M. macropus</taxonomicName>
. In the past some taxa (abbotti and macellus), now included under M. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF2B6A94F6F597D2176DBA9A" authorityName="Temminck" authorityYear="1840" box="[2313,2413,395,424]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="208" pageNumber="970" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="hasseltii">hasseltii</taxonomicName>
, have been treated as distinct species, treated as subspecies (continentis) of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF2B6A94F71D9783177CBAC5" baseAuthorityName="Horsfield" baseAuthorityYear="1824" box="[2273,2428,474,503]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="208" pageNumber="970" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="adversus">M. adversus</taxonomicName>
, or listed as subspecies (abbotti) under 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF2B6A94F6AD97A717EDB92D" baseAuthorityName="Horsfield" baseAuthorityYear="1824" box="[2385,2541,510,543]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="208" pageNumber="970" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="adversus">M. adversus</taxonomicName>
. A comprehensive study (including all subspecies across its distribution) is needed to resolve its limits within the current subspecies concept and relationship to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF2B6A94F64994C21459B98E" baseAuthorityName="Horsfield" baseAuthorityYear="1824" box="[2485,2649,667,700]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="208" pageNumber="970" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="adversus">M. adversus</taxonomicName>
. Four subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
